1. Moj pas se zove *Miki*. (*Miki* - my dog's name is Miki)
2. *Miki* je danas bio vrlo nestašan. (*Miki* - Miki was very naughty today)
3. Njegov nadimak je *Miki Maus*. (*Miki* - His nickname is Miki Mouse)
4. *Mikiju* se sviđa da trči u parku. (*Miki* - Miki likes to run in the park)
5. Moja sestra ima plišanog medu koji se zove *Miki*. (*Miki* - My sister has a stuffed bear named Miki)
6. Danas sam upoznao čovjeka čiji je nadimak *Miki*. (*Miki* - Today I met a man whose nickname is Miki)
7. *Miki* je najbolji prijatelj mog sina. (*Miki* - Miki is my son's best friend)
8. Naša omiljena pjesma je "Evo *Mikija*". (*Miki* - Our favorite song is "Here comes Miki")
9. *Mikijev* rođendan je sljedeći tjedan. (*Miki* - Miki's birthday is next week)
10. Naš pas je vrlo poslušan, ali *Miki* je najposlušniji. (*Miki* - Our dog is very obedient, but Miki is the most obedient)